{"tid":2169214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍準備在海南強力軍演 範圍含西沙群島","createTime":"2020-08-22T10:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T13:04:11.000Z","uid":337052,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"941b225a94437dfe54599930df59ad03903ef046","tid":2169214,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"海南周邊海域24日起6天軍演 範圍含西沙群島<br />\n最新更新：2020/08/22 15:58<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北22日電）中國海南省海事局22日下午在官網發布航行警告，宣布海南島東南部海域24日凌晨0時至29日午夜12時，進行軍事訓練活動。根據公告座標初步研判，軍演區域將涵蓋西沙群島。<br />\n<br />\n公告顯示，這次軍演座標範圍為：18-19.5N/111-13.5E、19-02.00N/112-14.5E、19-02.5N/112-57.0E、18-17.0N/113-51.5E、17-37.5N/113-52.0E、 16-38.00N/112-44.0E、16-38.00N/112-44.0E、16-38.00N/112-20.0E。<br />\n<br />\n公告稱，上述座標連線範圍內屆時將進行軍事訓練，禁止駛入。<br />\n<br />\n中共解放軍91208部隊、山東省海洋及漁業監督監察總隊、青島市海事局及連雲港市海事局昨天聯合公布，於今天中午12時起至26日，在青島至連雲港以東海域進行大型實彈射擊演習，期間禁止船舶進入臨時禁航區。（編輯：繆宗翰/周慧盈）1090822<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202008220132.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202008220132.aspx&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=9b6025b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202008220132.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTNp6yD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTNp6yD.png&h=3fe9d75e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e6a3485bd9d41d376edd10d0072801ee1a4d7e2","tid":2169214,"uid":10064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:13:31.000Z","msg":"哦，行過去睇下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d72c8e4d4604adbe5e2978878cd9a64db5f782","tid":2169214,"uid":95519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"唔知會唔會又有個颱風吹過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79bf05178886c8455dea83fb476cdb62c23a113","tid":2169214,"uid":54511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyT