":"2020-08-22T11:22:17.000Z","msg":"中國海南省海事局22日下午在官網發布航行警告，宣布海南島東南部海域24日凌晨0時至29日午夜12時，進行軍事訓練活動。"},{"pid":"d9de6312b2e2fc846cc1eb4e42c174e0c348f520","tid":2169214,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F162430_111a867613b72b01c436aec54f94ec97.png&amp;h=62bee876&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"df061d61e01a0007cc3807664534fc870ecbc615","tid":2169214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"台海軍情》禁航公告連發！ 中國南北端將同時軍演<br />\n   <br />\n中國官方昨天禁航公告連發，宣佈將在青島海域及南海海域同時進行軍演，圖為（左）中國海軍052型飛彈驅逐艦哈爾濱艦與（右）956EM型飛彈驅逐艦寧波艦2014年聯演。（美聯社）<br />\n中國官方昨天禁航公告連發，宣佈將在青島海域及南海海域同時進行軍演，圖為（左）中國海軍052型飛彈驅逐艦哈爾濱艦與（右）956EM型飛彈驅逐艦寧波艦2014年聯演。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-22 16:26:01<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國官方昨天禁航公告連發，除了公告從今天中午12時自下週三（26日）中午12時在青島至連雲港以東海域進行大型實彈射擊演習外，還公告24日起至29日將在海南島東南部海域進行軍演，儘管中共同時進行南北端海域軍演，但演習區域距離我國仍有一段距離。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，這份禁航通告是由中共海南海事局所發出，海南海事局昨天下午宣佈，下週一（24日）0時起至下週六（29日）晚間12時為止，將在南海海域進行軍演，並公告演習範圍，強調演訓期間禁止駛入。<br />\n<br />\n中國解放軍近來動作頻頻，中國國防部13日才宣布，將在台灣海峽及南北兩端舉行軍事演習，引發台美等國關注，而中國至昨天接連發出禁航公告，宣佈要在青島海域及南海海域同時進行軍演。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3268237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3268237&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=31d73751\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3268237&h=a596d2b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3268237</a>"},{"pid":"ef04cf331d2b4e3fb18146c2c123ae5a9125037f","tid":2169214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"美軍在東海佈下重兵，「台海北端軍演」悄悄結束了？中國官媒：解放軍三軍艦已完成「險象環生」的3日實彈演練<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/2963667?page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F2963667%3Fpage%3D1&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=1dfea5c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/2963667?page=1</a>"},{"pid":"27de9d6e41028e7efe77b498d5c2722be1473edc","tid":2169214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:37:53.000Z","msg":"【台海軍情】學者：美中對抗升溫 二戰後最緊張時刻<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200822/TMJHSS3J2NDIPMFS3CQXRMPRAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200822%2FTMJHSS3J2NDIPMFS3CQXRMPRAE%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=1a24de8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200822%2FTMJHSS3J2NDIPMFS3CQXRMPRAE%2F&h=1eefa9f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200822/TMJHSS3J2NDIPMFS3CQXRMPRAE/</a>"},{"pid":"e5c5874ad88367fbf6d0072d2bf289848647ac24","tid":2169214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:59:05.000Z","msg":"21日上午，中國官媒突然宣佈東海的編隊訓練課目已經結束，完成多型武器實射訓練，並稱這場演習「戰味十足，險象環生」。"},{"pid":"f38cf44c1bfea52917695616dff4aaefc241acd5","tid":2169214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"中共解放軍91208部隊、山東省海洋及漁業監督監察總隊、青島市海事局及連雲港市海事局昨天聯合公布，於今天中午12時起至26日，在青島至連雲港以東海域進行大型實彈射擊演習"},{"pid":"cf58389db31bc3cc5ea741c9f3a9488f975a8fed","tid":2169214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"紅二代開戰習近平 陸委會爆中共危機<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B4%85%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E7%88%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F-090025649.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F-090025649.html&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6XGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=a4e37d55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B4%85%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%A3%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E7%88%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F-090025649.html</a>"}]}